[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/thunderbolt">Thunderbolt</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/thunderbolt">Thunderbolt</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A strong electric blast is loosed at the foe. It may also leave the foe paralyzed.</p>